{"tid":1724184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我返工一個鐘，返屋企就要兩個鐘","createTime":"2019-11-15T11:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:16:36.000Z","uid":34160,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ff146efea4e805d5add154c0775df566d7cb5d","tid":1724184,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"一方面有人會提早返工，搞到個交通冇咁塞，但係放工就全部差唔多時間，逼撚死。另外，其實朝早係有唔少晨早特別車係會行西隧過海，朝早順到痴線。但係夜晚啲巴士主要行紅隧，搞到好多返屋企嘅巴士冇得搭，一係轉車，一係搭鐵。<br />\n<br />\n放工都算，但係我希望朝早可以被罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef36b4b7e930f8d2d2269d7057dbab2b6c70e83c","tid":1724184,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推好冇"},{"pid":"4fcdd2e531b6a0e487cbb0e4fedd4390ba816959","tid":1724184,"uid":235986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"有心就咪柒返啦"},{"pid":"d167e9e9da3a865d3030170fd457ac593058c372","tid":1724184,"uid":7183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"罷工係自由意志 無人拎支槍指住你返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ccf2c971e5c85e61453ef89ec27b506a4471f05","tid":1724184,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"屌我冇儲蓄，老閪都要返啦"},{"pid":"0ab795773ea5efb333af60cf1495ed8bf31d4dd2","tid":1724184,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"啲同事個撚個準時返工，早撚過我"}]}